WEBVTT

01:35.900 --> 01:40.980
=Love Beyond the Grave=
(Adapted from the novel by Li Qingran)

01:41.260 --> 01:43.980
=Episode 2=

01:49.940 --> 01:51.340
Stop running.

01:52.830 --> 01:53.750
Good boy.

01:54.030 --> 01:54.990
Come here.

01:55.470 --> 01:56.910
Come to Mother.

01:57.500 --> 01:58.340
Come over here.

02:10.460 --> 02:11.300
Captain Meng.

02:11.460 --> 02:12.790
It's her. She's creepy.

02:12.790 --> 02:13.630
She defied the curfew

02:13.740 --> 02:15.180
and killed several of our men.

02:21.580 --> 02:23.390
Get out of my way or die!

02:23.950 --> 02:25.420
Give me that boy!

02:26.020 --> 02:27.350
Take the boy and leave.

02:28.230 --> 02:29.740
- Let's go.
- He's mine.

02:30.110 --> 02:31.620
He's mine!

02:40.230 --> 02:41.790
(Why does my Spirits Lantern)

02:42.020 --> 02:44.070
(fear the Deliverance?)

02:53.550 --> 02:55.070
(I'm going to see)

02:55.420 --> 02:56.420
(what qualifies you)

02:56.420 --> 02:58.620
(as the master of the Deliverance.)

03:35.950 --> 03:37.070
Xiaoxiao!

03:42.860 --> 03:45.110
Give me back my boy!

03:45.180 --> 03:47.020
Xiaoxiao, help me!

03:47.700 --> 03:49.550
This boy is a real problem.

05:03.860 --> 05:04.860
Spare me.

05:05.300 --> 05:06.180
Please spare me.

05:06.260 --> 05:08.060
Forgive me for what I did.

05:08.740 --> 05:10.150
Spare me, please.

05:10.300 --> 05:12.010
Spare me.

05:12.550 --> 05:14.380
Please spare me.

05:14.620 --> 05:15.620
Please.

05:15.740 --> 05:16.740
Spare me.

05:18.620 --> 05:19.460
Where did she go?

05:19.590 --> 05:20.430
Um...

05:24.550 --> 05:25.390
Xiaoxiao.

05:29.180 --> 05:30.020
Keep him alive.

05:30.940 --> 05:31.780
Quickly.

05:50.380 --> 05:51.220
Chenying.

05:51.380 --> 05:52.350
Xiaoxiao.

05:53.470 --> 05:54.310
Chenying.

05:54.590 --> 05:56.110
Where have you been?

05:58.300 --> 05:59.940
You aren't going to abandon me, are you?

06:00.740 --> 06:01.860
Don't be ridiculous.

06:02.620 --> 06:03.940
I'm your only family now.

06:04.030 --> 06:05.500
Why would I abandon you?

06:06.420 --> 06:08.380
You really freaked me out.

06:23.620 --> 06:24.790
Thank you, Captain Meng,

06:24.910 --> 06:25.940
for saving the two of us.

06:26.470 --> 06:28.380
You're really a heroine,

06:28.550 --> 06:29.470
wise and valiant.

06:29.470 --> 06:30.710
What kind of sister are you?

06:30.970 --> 06:31.820
So late at night,

06:31.820 --> 06:32.660
he wandered alone.

06:32.740 --> 06:33.820
Didn't you know the curfew?

06:36.510 --> 06:38.290
I didn't see this coming.

06:38.800 --> 06:40.870
I just went out for a bit.

06:42.520 --> 06:44.670
I didn't know
it would turn out this way.

06:45.120 --> 06:45.960
If anything terrible

06:45.960 --> 06:48.110
really happened to Chenying...

06:53.110 --> 06:53.990
It's...

06:54.000 --> 06:55.670
It's not Xiaoxiao's fault.

06:55.990 --> 06:58.110
I... I sneaked out on my own.

06:58.820 --> 06:59.910
And I think

07:00.260 --> 07:01.710
that creepy creature

07:02.150 --> 07:03.790
was scared off by her.

07:05.710 --> 07:06.710
Nonsense.

07:07.380 --> 07:09.230
Captain Meng actually saved us.

07:09.230 --> 07:10.070
Or do you know

07:10.070 --> 07:11.230
what would have happened?

07:11.380 --> 07:12.550
Enough.

07:14.590 --> 07:15.670
It's all right now.

07:16.990 --> 07:17.840
It's so late.

07:17.910 --> 07:18.860
Let me walk you home.

07:20.420 --> 07:21.910
No need, Captain Meng.

07:22.710 --> 07:24.060
We live in the Prefect's Mansion.

07:24.500 --> 07:25.910
You live there?

07:26.550 --> 07:27.590
Isn't it assigned to...?

07:31.460 --> 07:32.930
So, you're the one

07:32.940 --> 07:34.250
who saved General Duan

07:34.740 --> 07:35.860
at the cemetery today.

07:42.180 --> 07:43.670
Yes, it was me.

07:43.740 --> 07:45.110
So, you're hostile.

07:45.940 --> 07:47.740
You try awfully hard
to get close to General.

07:47.860 --> 07:48.710
What are you up to?

07:48.820 --> 07:49.790
Who on earth are you?

07:50.150 --> 07:51.300
Captain Meng,

07:51.820 --> 07:53.380
I don't know the duke you mentioned.

07:53.470 --> 07:55.110
But if I had meant to hurt General Duan,

07:55.380 --> 07:56.350
during the assassination,

07:56.380 --> 07:57.420
I could have held him back

07:57.550 --> 07:59.060
and let him be killed, right?

07:59.790 --> 08:01.150
So, you want something else.

08:03.860 --> 08:04.700
That's right.

08:05.990 --> 08:07.150
I do want something else.

08:09.500 --> 08:10.740
That day, General Duan

08:11.230 --> 08:12.590
rescued people in Liangzhou

08:13.380 --> 08:15.550
like a god descending from the heavens.

08:17.260 --> 08:18.910
I fell in love with him at first sight.

08:19.550 --> 08:21.030
So, I tried hard to get close to him.

08:21.150 --> 08:22.060
You...

08:22.590 --> 08:23.910
He's from a distinguished family.

08:24.060 --> 08:25.500
Only ladies from Nandu are worthy.

08:25.820 --> 08:26.990
You're a mere country girl.

08:26.990 --> 08:27.910
Stop dreaming. You...

08:27.910 --> 08:28.750
Captain Meng,

08:29.420 --> 08:30.910
are you a lady from Nandu?

08:31.740 --> 08:32.620
Not exactly.

08:32.710 --> 08:33.590
There you have it.

08:33.830 --> 08:35.230
You're not a lady from Nandu.

08:35.260 --> 08:36.100
Neither am I.

08:36.260 --> 08:37.590
You can't marry Duan Xu.

08:37.780 --> 08:38.620
Neither can I.

08:38.860 --> 08:39.950
But you adore him.

08:40.110 --> 08:40.950
So do I.

08:41.110 --> 08:42.540
Then we have a common goal.

08:42.780 --> 08:44.500
So we're destined to meet

08:44.540 --> 08:45.990
and help each other.

08:46.740 --> 08:47.580
Aren't we?

08:47.830 --> 08:48.670
Meng.

08:52.740 --> 08:54.830
Xiaoxiao, you're gorgeous.

08:55.470 --> 08:57.540
You must be more worthy of the General.

08:57.660 --> 08:58.500
You...

08:59.470 --> 09:01.310
Captain Meng, thank you for tonight.

09:02.110 --> 09:02.950
But anyway,

09:03.500 --> 09:05.380
unless you have a magical tool,

09:05.430 --> 09:06.990
when you meet a filthy creature again,

09:07.110 --> 09:08.540
you'd better run away.

09:09.350 --> 09:11.350
After all, even the bravest sheep

09:11.900 --> 09:13.110
shouldn't fight a wolf.

09:13.590 --> 09:14.430
Right?

09:15.470 --> 09:16.310
Let's go.

09:21.950 --> 09:23.190
You must not run about again.

09:28.710 --> 09:29.740
City defense alarm?

09:31.190 --> 09:32.030
Move!

09:41.640 --> 09:42.490
He's there!

09:42.500 --> 09:43.340
After him!

09:43.380 --> 09:44.350
- Yes.
- Yes.

09:51.550 --> 09:53.140
After him! Don't let him get away!

09:53.830 --> 09:54.670
- Yes.
- Yes.

10:06.980 --> 10:10.820
(Han Lingqiu,
Defense Captain of Tabai Army)

10:14.900 --> 10:15.740
He killed himself.

10:19.190 --> 10:20.950
The army won't arrive until tomorrow.

10:21.230 --> 10:22.190
Why are you here?

10:22.470 --> 10:23.310
Why didn't you

10:23.470 --> 10:24.500
stop him from that?

10:41.350 --> 10:42.190
Spare me, Your Grace.

10:42.260 --> 10:43.190
Please spare me.

10:51.950 --> 10:52.830
(Shao Yinyin,)

10:53.310 --> 10:54.740
(a spirit from Shanling Temple.)

10:55.140 --> 10:56.500
(Her only obsession)

10:56.710 --> 10:58.310
(is with children.)

11:00.460 --> 11:01.180
(Token)

11:01.350 --> 11:02.380
Guan Huai.

11:05.590 --> 11:06.900
Greetings, Your Grace.

11:07.590 --> 11:09.310
As the Lord of Shanling Temple,

11:09.860 --> 11:11.260
do you see me as a tree?

11:12.700 --> 11:16.420
(Guan Huai, Lord of Shanling Temple)

11:20.780 --> 11:21.900
Oh, Your Grace.

11:22.140 --> 11:24.260
Sorry, I can't see clearly.

11:24.310 --> 11:25.740
I really can't.

11:26.900 --> 11:28.310
Since your hair is so long

11:28.350 --> 11:29.830
that it blocks your view,

11:29.950 --> 11:31.190
why don't you have it cut?

11:31.830 --> 11:33.350
No, no.

11:33.380 --> 11:34.350
Please don't do that.

11:35.070 --> 11:36.710
Your Grace, you know

11:36.900 --> 11:38.540
the hair of a spirit

11:38.620 --> 11:41.540
will not grow back once it's cut.

11:42.020 --> 11:42.860
So, I can't cut it.

11:43.430 --> 11:44.710
In the 32 Golden-wall Decrees,

11:44.710 --> 11:46.190
what is

11:46.900 --> 11:47.830
Article 3, Section 5?

11:49.590 --> 11:50.710
It's...

11:52.310 --> 11:53.540
No spirit shall store up

11:53.590 --> 11:55.620
the spirit flames of children under ten.

11:56.380 --> 11:57.350
Looks like the decrees

11:57.380 --> 11:59.020
don't apply to the Lord

11:59.710 --> 12:01.230
of Shanling Temple.

12:07.620 --> 12:08.620
Fang Chang!

12:09.260 --> 12:10.470
Fang Chang!

12:12.180 --> 12:13.020
Greetings, Your Grace.

12:13.020 --> 12:13.940
(Fang Chang,
Vice Lord of Shanling Temple)

12:14.430 --> 12:15.270
Greetings, My Lord.

12:19.470 --> 12:21.260
I trusted you.

12:21.350 --> 12:22.710
During my seclusion,

12:23.020 --> 12:25.020
I entrusted you with all the affairs

12:25.110 --> 12:26.260
of our temple.

12:26.660 --> 12:28.190
How could you

12:29.020 --> 12:30.310
neglect your duties like that?

12:30.660 --> 12:32.990
You... You...

12:33.310 --> 12:35.310
You're like playing a game,

12:35.430 --> 12:36.710
passing the buck.

12:37.140 --> 12:38.350
Please show some mercy

12:38.500 --> 12:39.340
and let Yinyin go.

12:40.230 --> 12:41.070
She stored up

12:41.080 --> 12:42.860
the flames of six children under ten.

12:43.830 --> 12:45.110
How should she be punished?

12:45.830 --> 12:47.430
She didn't mean to defy you, Your Grace.

12:47.900 --> 12:48.900
Her obsession

12:48.950 --> 12:49.790
is with children.

12:49.830 --> 12:51.140
She couldn't control herself.

12:51.470 --> 12:53.230
These things are clearly recorded

12:53.230 --> 12:54.780
in the Book of Spirits.

12:55.140 --> 12:56.860
You don't need to repeat them.

12:57.590 --> 12:59.830
I don't care if she meant to defy me.

13:01.780 --> 13:04.230
But as long as I hold this position,

13:05.430 --> 13:06.620
no one shall defy

13:10.020 --> 13:11.380
my decrees.

13:22.260 --> 13:23.990
There's a saying in the Mortal World.

13:25.830 --> 13:27.540
"Spoiling a child ruins him."

13:29.380 --> 13:30.540
It's the same

13:31.190 --> 13:32.230
with lovers.

13:38.230 --> 13:40.020
Since she's a spirit of Shanling Temple,

13:40.860 --> 13:42.140
you will deal with her.

13:44.500 --> 13:45.740
As for you,

13:47.900 --> 13:49.350
go to Yan Ke and get punished.

13:50.190 --> 13:51.350
Yes, Your Grace.

13:51.740 --> 13:54.070
Farewell, Your Grace.

14:07.190 --> 14:08.660
Oh, look at you.

14:09.310 --> 14:10.150
Chang,

14:10.500 --> 14:11.340
help me.

14:13.740 --> 14:14.830
Oh, My Lord.

14:15.540 --> 14:16.900
You're the eldest in our world.

14:16.990 --> 14:18.350
Her Grace respects you.

14:18.660 --> 14:19.540
I'm begging you.

14:19.710 --> 14:20.830
Please plead for Yinyin.

14:20.960 --> 14:21.800
I'll do anything

14:21.800 --> 14:22.950
to repay your kindness.

14:23.020 --> 14:24.260
You're grabbing my hair.

14:24.540 --> 14:25.590
Let go!

14:27.590 --> 14:28.430
You're right.

14:28.950 --> 14:31.110
I'm over 3,000 years older.

14:31.470 --> 14:32.310
So what?

14:32.900 --> 14:35.430
He Simu wasn't even 100 years old

14:36.190 --> 14:38.260
when she defeated the rebellion

14:38.380 --> 14:39.900
with a bloodbath in the 24 Temples.

14:40.230 --> 14:41.830
30% of the lords

14:41.900 --> 14:44.140
were killed by her.

14:44.470 --> 14:45.380
And all those lords

14:45.540 --> 14:47.540
were far older than her.

14:51.350 --> 14:52.710
She's the most talented sovereign

14:53.020 --> 14:54.710
within ten generations.

14:55.590 --> 14:57.070
I can't afford to displease her.

15:13.430 --> 15:14.710
It's been 400 years.

15:16.350 --> 15:18.350
I've never seen you so cowardly.

15:21.140 --> 15:22.000
In the Void,

15:22.010 --> 15:23.380
you're the most powerful tool.

15:31.950 --> 15:33.020
- Turn it over.
- Here.

15:33.260 --> 15:34.100
Pull it tight.

15:35.860 --> 15:37.620
Last night, the army
arrived ahead of time.

15:38.260 --> 15:39.100
So, this morning,

15:39.350 --> 15:40.430
I'm here to report.

15:41.350 --> 15:42.540
If the army was in town,

15:43.070 --> 15:44.070
why did you turn up alone

15:44.500 --> 15:45.620
below the city wall

15:45.660 --> 15:46.590
last night?

15:47.140 --> 15:48.430
Last night, I heard some noise

15:49.230 --> 15:50.950
and went there to check around.

15:52.880 --> 15:53.720
Today,

15:53.720 --> 15:54.860
I have defense work to do.

15:56.590 --> 15:57.430
I'll take my leave.

16:03.780 --> 16:04.620
Xu,

16:04.780 --> 16:05.620
about last night,

16:05.830 --> 16:07.070
do you also suspect him?

16:07.140 --> 16:08.740
That assassin knew our defense well.

16:09.110 --> 16:10.070
Han Lingqiu should have

16:10.190 --> 16:11.350
easily captured him.

16:11.500 --> 16:13.030
How come he managed to kill himself?

16:13.540 --> 16:14.380
Unless...

16:14.470 --> 16:15.900
Han Lingqiu colluded with him.

16:23.990 --> 16:25.020
According to my lists,

16:25.350 --> 16:26.540
prepare supplies and armaments

16:26.590 --> 16:27.430
for the whole army.

16:27.830 --> 16:28.670
Yes.

16:31.860 --> 16:33.660
What have you got about Miss He?

16:34.540 --> 16:35.900
Xu, I asked around.

16:36.660 --> 16:37.620
He Xiaoxiao

16:37.780 --> 16:39.230
claims to be a local.

16:39.620 --> 16:41.350
But nobody in town knows about her.

16:41.450 --> 16:42.300
And nobody has heard

16:42.310 --> 16:43.830
about her from Xue Chenying's father.

16:44.470 --> 16:46.020
She has no relatives in town.

16:46.260 --> 16:48.070
She said Xue Chenying's father

16:48.070 --> 16:49.470
saved her by giving her a meal,

16:49.590 --> 16:50.660
so she takes care of him.

16:53.310 --> 16:54.150
A meal?

16:55.350 --> 16:56.190
As you instructed,

16:56.190 --> 16:57.780
I asked her about weather changes.

16:58.020 --> 16:59.070
She predicted accurately.

16:59.230 --> 17:00.740
Accurate even to the hour.

17:01.310 --> 17:03.430
The wind strength and direction
were correct, too.

17:08.260 --> 17:09.740
When it was pitch dark

17:10.060 --> 17:11.260
and nobody was around,

17:11.780 --> 17:13.630
if a child traveled all alone,

17:13.870 --> 17:15.740
a spirit that preyed on children

17:15.740 --> 17:16.630
would appear and hunt.

17:17.470 --> 17:19.150
That spirit looked young and beautiful.

17:19.470 --> 17:20.950
But her eyes were totally black.

17:21.230 --> 17:22.230
She was holding

17:22.340 --> 17:24.150
such a big jar.

17:27.470 --> 17:29.300
Blood was dripping on the ground.

17:30.300 --> 17:31.230
Suddenly,

17:31.630 --> 17:33.060
she grew fangs,

17:33.060 --> 17:34.340
reached out long nails,

17:34.340 --> 17:35.500
opened her big mouth,

17:35.580 --> 17:36.630
and bit that child.

17:40.340 --> 17:41.340
Miss,

17:41.710 --> 17:43.470
do spirits really exist?

17:43.950 --> 17:45.580
Are they scary?

17:48.820 --> 17:50.350
Spirits are just like humans.

17:50.470 --> 17:51.580
Some are good, some are bad.

17:51.910 --> 17:53.190
But I must warn you.

17:53.630 --> 17:54.500
If you meet

17:54.500 --> 17:55.630
any strange guys,

17:55.780 --> 17:57.540
especially those who have dark eyes

17:57.540 --> 17:58.740
with no whites at all...

17:58.950 --> 17:59.870
To be safe,

18:00.060 --> 18:01.020
run immediately.

18:01.190 --> 18:02.030
Got it?

18:02.500 --> 18:03.340
Then...

18:03.740 --> 18:04.630
Is there anything

18:04.630 --> 18:05.710
they're scared of?

18:06.740 --> 18:08.060
My father told me

18:08.710 --> 18:11.230
they were scared of magical tools

18:11.470 --> 18:12.430
and their leader,

18:12.540 --> 18:13.380
Sovereign of Spirits.

18:13.430 --> 18:14.270
Sovereign?

18:14.390 --> 18:15.580
Like an emperor?

18:16.710 --> 18:17.550
Something like that.

18:18.100 --> 18:19.870
The legendary Void Spirit World

18:20.260 --> 18:21.300
is under the Sovereign.

18:22.340 --> 18:23.300
General?

18:30.060 --> 18:30.900
Greetings.

18:32.190 --> 18:33.470
You're so knowledgeable, Miss He.

18:34.470 --> 18:35.310
I'm impressed.

18:36.990 --> 18:39.710
They're bowing for marriage!

18:40.390 --> 18:42.870
Wedding time!

18:43.150 --> 18:44.300
General, in you go.

18:44.630 --> 18:47.190
Wedding time! Wedding time!

18:47.470 --> 18:50.150
Wedding time!

18:50.580 --> 18:52.100
Did you forget what I just told you?

19:16.190 --> 19:17.300
Since I came to town,

19:17.870 --> 19:18.710
you seem to have been

19:19.060 --> 19:19.950
quite interested

19:19.950 --> 19:20.790
in my sword.

19:22.540 --> 19:23.870
A great sword deserves a hero.

19:24.230 --> 19:25.500
I just want to know

19:25.740 --> 19:26.670
where you managed

19:26.670 --> 19:27.670
to get this sword.

19:28.260 --> 19:29.580
That's a long story.

19:30.670 --> 19:31.630
One day, on a bridge

19:31.630 --> 19:32.470
of Nandu,

19:32.870 --> 19:33.990
I met an old man.

19:34.910 --> 19:36.020
He said my unique physique

19:36.470 --> 19:37.430
made me a rare talent

19:37.430 --> 19:38.270
for martial arts.

19:38.870 --> 19:40.190
So, he gave me this sword.

19:41.150 --> 19:42.870
He even said the sword's affinity for me

19:43.670 --> 19:44.740
would make me an immortal.

19:48.630 --> 19:49.910
Congratulations, General,

19:50.020 --> 19:51.260
on having this great sword.

19:53.980 --> 19:55.090
The jade at your waist

19:55.370 --> 19:56.210
looks unique, too.

19:57.470 --> 19:58.630
It somewhat resembles

19:58.630 --> 19:59.580
my plum tree.

20:00.580 --> 20:02.540
Where did you get it?

20:03.580 --> 20:04.580
May I have a look?

20:14.200 --> 20:15.050
It's just

20:15.050 --> 20:16.430
something unremarkable.

20:18.180 --> 20:19.910
To what do I owe this pleasure?

20:20.820 --> 20:21.870
Today, I'm here

20:22.780 --> 20:23.870
to ask you for a favor.

20:25.190 --> 20:26.030
I know

20:26.340 --> 20:27.390
you can predict weather.

20:28.740 --> 20:29.990
I wonder if you would like

20:31.080 --> 20:31.930
to observe the weather

20:31.940 --> 20:32.870
for my army.

20:35.670 --> 20:37.540
What exactly do you want to know?

20:38.630 --> 20:39.470
Do you know

20:40.260 --> 20:41.100
which nights will

20:41.100 --> 20:41.950
have an east wind?

20:42.470 --> 20:43.540
The stronger, the better.

20:44.190 --> 20:45.300
Snow would be the best.

20:47.020 --> 20:47.910
Night.

20:48.430 --> 20:49.390
East wind.

20:51.300 --> 20:52.190
It's a low-lying place

20:52.260 --> 20:53.230
with crowded houses.

20:53.340 --> 20:54.390
Wind can be blocked.

20:55.230 --> 20:56.670
General, do you mind taking me up

20:57.300 --> 20:58.950
to the city wall for wind observation?

20:59.580 --> 21:00.430
Up to the city wall?

21:01.540 --> 21:03.060
That's a key location for city defense.

21:03.910 --> 21:04.950
So, General, do you dare

21:05.430 --> 21:06.910
to take me up there?

21:12.230 --> 21:13.070
All right.

21:13.740 --> 21:14.670
I'll take you up there.

21:19.460 --> 21:20.890
Xiaoxiao, in that case,

21:20.900 --> 21:21.950
put on your cloak.

21:24.230 --> 21:25.190
Clever boy.

21:25.870 --> 21:26.720
Otherwise,

21:26.820 --> 21:27.820
I would freeze again.

21:29.100 --> 21:30.150
The fresh sugar figure.

21:30.230 --> 21:31.300
Xiaoxiao made it herself.

21:31.390 --> 21:32.630
General, when you go up

21:32.630 --> 21:33.470
to the city wall,

21:33.470 --> 21:34.670
you can share it.

21:39.630 --> 21:40.470
Miss He,

21:41.430 --> 21:42.270
there you go.

21:50.620 --> 21:56.300
(North Gate, Liangzhou)

21:57.670 --> 21:58.510
What's wrong, Miss?

22:00.020 --> 22:01.150
It's too high.

22:01.910 --> 22:03.020
I can't get up there.

22:03.500 --> 22:04.390
But you proposed

22:04.390 --> 22:05.430
that we should go up there.

22:05.820 --> 22:07.300
But it's too high.

22:07.910 --> 22:09.150
It makes me nervous.

22:09.990 --> 22:11.190
I've always been weak.

22:11.670 --> 22:13.190
I really can't make it up there.

22:15.670 --> 22:16.780
Actually, I figured

22:17.020 --> 22:18.260
you would have this problem.

22:20.180 --> 22:21.580
(North Gate, Liangzhou)

22:26.300 --> 22:27.140
Get on that, please.

22:31.710 --> 22:33.430
That's too bumpy.

22:34.150 --> 22:35.300
I don't like it, either.

22:36.470 --> 22:38.100
If you don't want to take it,

22:39.300 --> 22:40.780
I'll have to carry you up there.

23:06.150 --> 23:06.990
As expected, up here,

23:06.990 --> 23:08.260
every wisp of wind can be seen.

23:08.500 --> 23:09.910
Scattered and dense,

23:10.710 --> 23:12.820
it blows all over like white cobwebs.

23:17.870 --> 23:18.820
Its origin is unknown,

23:19.710 --> 23:20.910
and so is its destination.

23:22.630 --> 23:23.910
Like white cobwebs?

23:24.780 --> 23:26.230
Sounds peculiar.

23:27.580 --> 23:28.420
White wind.

23:29.680 --> 23:31.470
Just like the color of my cuff?

23:33.740 --> 23:34.580
Yes.

23:41.260 --> 23:42.190
After you die,

23:42.740 --> 23:44.340
I'll take care of your sword.

23:45.390 --> 23:46.300
In exchange,

23:46.740 --> 23:48.060
I grant you a wish.

23:48.630 --> 23:49.580
I will fulfill

23:49.670 --> 23:50.670
one last wish of yours.

23:51.230 --> 23:52.070
Last wish?

23:54.100 --> 23:54.940
Just a wish.

23:57.430 --> 23:58.340
I won't ask you

23:58.340 --> 23:59.580
how you can fulfill my wish.

23:59.910 --> 24:01.260
But what you said just now...

24:02.100 --> 24:02.940
It sounds like

24:03.100 --> 24:03.950
I am going

24:03.950 --> 24:04.990
to die.

24:05.990 --> 24:07.060
Aren't you?

24:08.910 --> 24:10.230
Seen from here,

24:10.470 --> 24:11.630
it's the way to Shuozhou.

24:12.470 --> 24:13.870
You make me observe the wind

24:13.990 --> 24:15.630
because you will cross the Guanhe River

24:15.910 --> 24:16.910
and attack Shuozhou.

24:20.950 --> 24:21.790
I'm impressed.

24:22.670 --> 24:23.820
You guessed right.

24:24.260 --> 24:26.060
If you rashly lead your army out,

24:26.740 --> 24:28.060
you won't be fighting,

24:28.740 --> 24:30.060
but you'll be dying.

24:35.060 --> 24:36.470
So, what is your wish?

24:40.540 --> 24:41.540
My wish is

24:42.500 --> 24:43.950
the 17 Prefectures
north of the Guanhe River

24:45.100 --> 24:46.390
will return to Great Liang.

24:57.340 --> 24:58.870
Life-and-death struggles...

24:59.470 --> 25:01.020
Ambitions to regain lost land...

25:01.260 --> 25:02.630
Such boring things.

25:03.260 --> 25:05.020
Why take them so seriously?

25:06.710 --> 25:08.060
Your words remind me of something.

25:09.190 --> 25:10.030
When I was little,

25:10.030 --> 25:11.430
I loved building beach sandcastles.

25:13.430 --> 25:14.870
But however well I built them,

25:15.340 --> 25:16.540
the rising tides

25:16.740 --> 25:17.670
would wash them away.

25:18.140 --> 25:19.820
If I had had your insight,

25:20.470 --> 25:21.950
I wouldn't have been that sad.

25:24.190 --> 25:25.190
But anyway, sandcastles

25:25.340 --> 25:26.540
didn't truly disappear.

25:27.540 --> 25:28.710
They became the sand again.

25:30.740 --> 25:31.870
Maybe you're like me

25:32.580 --> 25:33.740
and I'm like a sandcastle.

25:35.300 --> 25:36.470
I used to be sand.

25:38.060 --> 25:38.990
I will be sand.

25:39.910 --> 25:41.260
For one moment, I'm a sandcastle.

25:43.540 --> 25:45.500
And I only live for this moment.

26:00.260 --> 26:01.500
Do you have to go?

26:04.340 --> 26:05.870
Now, only by fighting war with war

26:07.300 --> 26:08.230
and seeking peace in war

26:09.030 --> 26:09.870
can our people

26:09.870 --> 26:11.430
and those in North Chong stop fighting

26:12.390 --> 26:13.260
and achieve peace.

26:16.230 --> 26:17.500
This is my wish.

26:18.100 --> 26:18.940
If possible,

26:20.740 --> 26:22.020
please help me fulfill it.

26:37.630 --> 26:38.470
Miss He,

26:39.300 --> 26:40.500
who is this sugar figure?

26:41.470 --> 26:42.310
Shen Shu.

26:42.950 --> 26:43.800
Days ago, Chenying

26:43.800 --> 26:44.890
encountered strange things.

26:44.890 --> 26:45.730
He was really scared.

26:46.100 --> 26:47.010
So, I asked Meng

26:47.010 --> 26:47.870
for some malt sugar

26:47.990 --> 26:48.870
and made the Door God.

26:49.300 --> 26:50.540
I heard evil spirits fear him.

26:50.870 --> 26:51.870
It works for exorcism.

26:56.190 --> 26:57.030
How about

26:57.990 --> 26:58.830
you try some?

27:18.060 --> 27:18.900
Miss He,

27:19.710 --> 27:20.550
this sugar figure

27:20.820 --> 27:21.660
tastes too sweet.

27:24.470 --> 27:25.310
It is?

27:25.950 --> 27:26.790
Way too sweet.

27:30.190 --> 27:31.230
I have a sweet tooth.

27:42.190 --> 27:43.030
Xiaoxiao,

27:43.150 --> 27:44.190
the lady next door

27:44.470 --> 27:45.390
gave me Dingsheng Cake.

27:45.820 --> 27:46.660
Have a taste.

27:46.670 --> 27:47.510
It's very sweet.

28:04.430 --> 28:05.710
Be careful, Xiaoxiao. It's hot.

28:12.740 --> 28:13.580
Oh, so sweet.

28:16.870 --> 28:17.710
So sweet.

28:22.300 --> 28:24.300
Which is sweeter,

28:24.640 --> 28:25.500
my sugar figure

28:25.500 --> 28:26.430
or this cake?

28:27.260 --> 28:28.780
This cake, of course.

28:31.020 --> 28:32.230
But Xiaoxiao,

28:32.630 --> 28:34.100
your sugar figure tastes great, too.

28:34.540 --> 28:35.580
It's not very sweet,

28:35.670 --> 28:36.740
but I love it.

28:39.870 --> 28:40.710
Not very sweet?

28:41.990 --> 28:43.670
Not as sweet as this cake.

28:44.470 --> 28:46.390
(Chenying is from a poor family.)

28:47.060 --> 28:48.630
(He hasn't had too much sweet food.)

28:49.100 --> 28:50.150
(He thinks it's not sweet,)

28:50.630 --> 28:52.020
(so it can't be sweet.)

28:52.910 --> 28:53.750
It is?

28:54.540 --> 28:55.380
Way too sweet.

29:03.340 --> 29:04.260
Today,

29:05.230 --> 29:06.580
what is the color

29:06.780 --> 29:07.710
of General Duan's cuff?

29:09.870 --> 29:10.710
Blue.

29:11.470 --> 29:12.340
White wind.

29:13.540 --> 29:15.390
Just like the color of my cuff?

29:16.820 --> 29:17.660
Yes.

29:21.470 --> 29:22.870
(What a cunning man.)

29:23.300 --> 29:25.300
(How dare he probe me?)

29:30.710 --> 29:31.910
It's a fine day today.

29:32.190 --> 29:33.030
You go out and play.

29:33.820 --> 29:34.660
Really?

29:45.260 --> 29:46.100
Great Ancestor.

29:47.230 --> 29:48.470
I remember you told me

29:48.990 --> 29:50.340
Duan Xu grew up in Nandu

29:50.580 --> 29:51.630
until he was twelve

29:51.990 --> 29:53.190
and was sent back to Daizhou

29:53.190 --> 29:54.260
to serve his grandmother

29:54.580 --> 29:56.100
before he returned at the age of 19.

29:56.630 --> 29:57.470
That's right.

29:58.390 --> 29:59.500
There's no sea in Nandu.

30:00.440 --> 30:01.290
Daizhou is

30:01.300 --> 30:02.630
even farther from the sea.

30:03.390 --> 30:04.710
So, where did he see the sea?

30:05.010 --> 30:05.850
When I was little,

30:05.870 --> 30:07.260
I loved building beach sandcastles.

30:08.060 --> 30:09.430
And on which beach

30:09.780 --> 30:10.820
did he build sandcastles?

30:12.580 --> 30:13.740
Something's wrong with him.

30:14.710 --> 30:15.780
Look him up thoroughly.

30:27.710 --> 30:29.190
Give it to me.

30:29.300 --> 30:31.230
Pass it to me.

30:32.960 --> 30:33.800
Here.

30:33.820 --> 30:34.670
To me!

30:34.740 --> 30:36.190
- Hurry!
- Pass it to me!

30:36.190 --> 30:39.910
- Me, me!
- Give it to me!

30:40.390 --> 30:41.540
Thank you, sir.

30:42.630 --> 30:45.230
What makes you so happy?

30:45.430 --> 30:46.300
Today, I got to know

30:46.300 --> 30:47.340
a very interesting friend.

30:48.020 --> 30:49.020
She can see the wind,

30:49.340 --> 30:50.820
but she probably can't see colors,

30:51.230 --> 30:52.070
feel the temperature,

30:52.670 --> 30:53.510
or have five senses.

30:54.300 --> 30:56.020
And she's faking her identity.

31:10.950 --> 31:12.670
Isn't she terrifying?

31:13.580 --> 31:14.420
Terrifying?

31:15.060 --> 31:15.910
Not at all.

31:16.630 --> 31:17.820
I think she's interesting.

31:23.990 --> 31:24.830
General.

31:28.390 --> 31:29.230
Duan Xu!

31:29.820 --> 31:31.470
Want your own man to be the commandant?

31:31.580 --> 31:33.020
I'll be the first to object!

31:33.140 --> 31:34.700
(Wu Shengliu, Captain of Tabai Army)

31:34.710 --> 31:35.550
Commandant Wu,

31:36.230 --> 31:37.990
you've been busy training the soldiers.

31:38.340 --> 31:39.180
Hard work, indeed.

31:39.950 --> 31:41.390
I have something to discuss with you.

31:42.060 --> 31:43.950
Shall we talk over tea?

31:45.470 --> 31:46.310
You...

31:49.740 --> 31:50.580
He...

31:58.100 --> 31:58.940
Let's go.

31:59.670 --> 32:00.630
All right. Be careful.

32:03.540 --> 32:05.180
Xiaoxiao, Xiaoxiao.

32:07.020 --> 32:07.860
The General is having

32:07.860 --> 32:08.990
a very rude visitor.

32:09.100 --> 32:10.340
I think they're about to fight.

32:15.070 --> 32:16.550
Shall we go and watch?

32:20.630 --> 32:21.630
The army has settled in.

32:22.990 --> 32:24.430
I'll promote a captain to commandant.

32:24.820 --> 32:25.820
Duan Shunxi,

32:27.040 --> 32:28.410
(Strict Enforcement)
do you think

32:28.410 --> 32:29.790
this is your own army?

32:30.100 --> 32:31.670
We've just recaptured Liangzhou.

32:32.060 --> 32:32.950
Why are you desperate

32:32.950 --> 32:34.340
to plant your own man in the army?

32:41.060 --> 32:41.950
Perfect timing.

32:44.190 --> 32:45.030
Have a bite.

32:46.710 --> 32:48.150
Xiaoxiao, when we're here,

32:48.150 --> 32:49.630
will General see us?

32:49.780 --> 32:50.620
No.

32:50.950 --> 32:51.950
This is magic.

32:52.190 --> 32:53.030
He can't see us.

32:55.190 --> 32:57.020
Our troops didn't fight wars for years.

32:57.710 --> 32:58.580
Discipline was slack.

32:58.990 --> 33:00.990
Soldiers often fled
when facing North Chong Army.

33:02.670 --> 33:04.150
When I first took over Taibai Army,

33:04.430 --> 33:05.270
it was no different.

33:05.910 --> 33:07.020
Captain Meng and Captain Xia

33:07.020 --> 33:07.910
assisted me.

33:08.260 --> 33:09.260
We rectified discipline,

33:09.540 --> 33:10.990
and became the famous Tabai Army

33:10.990 --> 33:12.740
that finally recaptured Liangzhou.

33:12.950 --> 33:14.150
I'm not convinced, anyway.

33:14.540 --> 33:16.540
Commandant Wu, do you favor Captain Han?

33:17.430 --> 33:18.270
Han Lingqiu,

33:18.780 --> 33:19.670
what do you think?

33:22.150 --> 33:22.990
Han,

33:23.580 --> 33:24.870
I'll tell them

33:24.910 --> 33:26.260
what you're too embarrassed to say.

33:26.950 --> 33:27.820
General Duan,

33:28.710 --> 33:30.340
Han should have been the commandant

33:30.740 --> 33:32.430
instead of you.

33:32.580 --> 33:33.420
And look.

33:33.710 --> 33:35.100
Now you're the general,

33:35.670 --> 33:37.630
and you want to promote your own man.

33:37.870 --> 33:39.390
If you insist,

33:39.950 --> 33:40.790
ask your man

33:40.910 --> 33:41.750
to fight me.

33:42.230 --> 33:43.080
If he wins,

33:43.150 --> 33:43.990
he'll be promoted.

33:44.230 --> 33:45.070
If he loses,

33:45.580 --> 33:47.020
he'll end up in the mass grave!

33:47.100 --> 33:48.780
Since you're keen on fights,

33:49.340 --> 33:50.470
will you fight me?

33:54.580 --> 33:55.420
You?

33:56.390 --> 33:57.300
Well, General,

33:57.910 --> 33:59.390
don't go back on your word.

34:01.150 --> 34:02.190
Wu Shengliu is famous

34:02.670 --> 34:03.510
for infinite strength

34:03.870 --> 34:05.020
and superb martial arts.

34:05.530 --> 34:06.710
General may not defeat him.

34:08.710 --> 34:10.350
General accepted the challenge.

34:11.040 --> 34:12.210
He must have a plan.

34:17.620 --> 34:19.870
General will fight that man.

34:20.270 --> 34:21.620
That man looks much stronger

34:21.620 --> 34:22.580
than General.

34:22.950 --> 34:24.500
He looks fierce, too.

34:25.310 --> 34:27.020
I'm sure he has superb martial arts.

34:28.750 --> 34:30.310
Commandant Wu is going to lose.

34:33.350 --> 34:34.190
Why?

34:34.870 --> 34:36.180
He's stronger.

34:37.390 --> 34:38.790
His skull doesn't look good.

34:42.910 --> 34:43.750
Skull...

34:43.870 --> 34:47.700
Does it have anything to do
with martial arts?

34:48.500 --> 34:49.340
Yes.

34:50.180 --> 34:51.990
One with a pretty skull

34:52.470 --> 34:53.310
is hard to kill.

35:06.140 --> 35:06.980
Commandant Wu.

35:06.980 --> 35:09.100
(Strict Enforcement)

35:09.100 --> 35:10.060
Bring it on.

35:19.100 --> 35:19.940
General,

35:20.140 --> 35:20.980
pull out your sword.

35:21.500 --> 35:22.790
When it's time to pull it out,

35:23.270 --> 35:24.350
I'll pull it out.

35:26.180 --> 35:27.500
I'll start, then.

35:28.270 --> 35:29.110
Watch this!

35:44.500 --> 35:47.140
This young general moves so swiftly.

35:51.100 --> 35:52.620
Especially his eyes.

36:10.910 --> 36:12.220
Commandant Wu, I didn't know

36:12.220 --> 36:13.390
you could defend...

36:16.100 --> 36:16.940
So nimbly.

36:51.310 --> 36:52.150
You...

36:52.990 --> 36:53.830
(What is wrong?)

37:21.220 --> 37:22.580
(He has such sharp eyes)

37:22.830 --> 37:23.950
(and keen ears.)

37:25.100 --> 37:26.620
(A gentleman from Nandu)

37:26.620 --> 37:27.660
(can't have such skills.)

37:57.870 --> 38:00.020
(I believe he has killed many people.)

38:00.990 --> 38:03.350
(More than these military officers have.)

38:18.601 --> 38:23.931
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

38:24.261 --> 38:28.511
♪Light encountered shadow♪

38:29.871 --> 38:35.241
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

38:35.541 --> 38:40.141
♪The unbreakable fate♪

38:41.231 --> 38:43.071
♪Suddenly cracked♪

38:55.281 --> 39:00.721
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

39:00.901 --> 39:05.231
♪Light encountered shadow♪

39:06.601 --> 39:11.991
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

39:12.221 --> 39:16.161
♪The unbreakable fate♪

39:17.931 --> 39:19.821
♪Suddenly cracked♪

39:22.481 --> 39:25.641
♪Listen, all sounds are roaring♪

39:25.641 --> 39:28.171
♪As cold ice turns into tides♪

39:28.171 --> 39:33.691
♪A century's loneliness melts dreams♪

39:33.691 --> 39:36.931
♪Following fate's guidance♪

39:36.931 --> 39:41.791
♪By fate, our moments were exchanged♪

39:42.131 --> 39:45.151
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪

39:45.151 --> 39:47.971
♪Watch fireworks fall like stars♪

39:48.231 --> 39:50.761
♪This bond is tangled into a thread♪

39:50.761 --> 39:56.181
♪Worldly reflections fade into mist♪

39:56.351 --> 39:59.421
♪Borrowing one fleeting heartbeat♪

39:59.581 --> 40:04.481
♪You drew me into mortal dust,
till I'm enamored with its charms♪

40:04.691 --> 40:08.161
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪
